Known issues
------------

- The image description status bar is not cleared sometimes
  * Note that this may have been solved in version 0.8, but
    I'm not sure enough

If you happen to find a bug, please create a new issue at
<https://github.com/robtimus/bbbm/issues>, or mail me at
<bbbm@icemanx.nl>.
Don't forget to mention the bbbm version.
